      question: "What was the best part of being on a boat?",
      answer:
        "This will vary for each individual. Having a greater impact than many\nothers, the continued learning, the responsibility, having higher\nquality shipmates, an atmosphere of less formality, doing much more\ninteresting work, or professional satisfaction -- what's your personal\npreference? Better pay and better food help morale but aren't usually\nthe primary motivators in the long run.",
      category_id: 6,
      category_name: "Who Were the Crews Aboard WW2 US Subs",
